'''Arthur Baker''' is the calligrapher for [[William C. Dietz]]' [[Star Wars: Dark Forces (novellas)|''Dark Forces'']] series of novellas.

==Biography==
Arthur Baker was born on the West Coast, and as of [[2005]], lives in Andover, Massachusetts. As a renowned calligrapher, he has designed many [[Wikipedia:Typeface|typefaces]] and published over twenty books on the subject. Examples of his work include the use of his Signet Bold font for the "Coke" on Coca-Cola products and his ITC Tiepolo on Lipton products.

